{
  "text": "Remark 4.2. This result is proved in [CITATION_1] in the monodimensional setting. In [10, Proposition 4.1], it is proved in the multidimensional setting that U \u2212 and U + are flux-limited solutions but it is not proved that the corresponding flux functions are precisely H T and H reg T . The fact that the flux function corresponding to U + is H reg T is proved in [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
